  "texts": [
    "The system's effectiveness is evaluated using a dataset comprising 936 words, resulting in an impressive accuracy rate of 98.71%.",
    "Elsayed and Elghazaly [58] developed a system that enhanced named entities recognition for Arabic using the existing technology used for Arabic nouns and entity extractions.",
    "They have implemented using Rule Based approach in which the method extracts Arabic nouns in accordance with Arabic grammar rules in cases when Arabic grammar rules algorithms have identified Arabic nouns that are useless in gazetteers.",
    "Pushpalatha and Thanamani [59] discussed the name of Kannada text document which includes several NEs are Name of place, person, designation and organization etc.",
    "The author used multi-SVM classification for describing the name NER Rule-based Approach Machine Learning Approach Deep Learning ApproachHybrid Approach entities of Kannada."
